# Digital Guide

Starter repository for the NTO Smart City case "Digital Guide".

## Quick start

```bash
python -m venv .venv
.venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -e .[dev]
uvicorn digital_guide.main:app --reload
```

## Main folders

- `configs/` runtime configuration
- `src/digital_guide/` local server
- `firmware/` ESP32 starter firmware
- `tests/` unit and integration tests

